column12: Welcome to The RMHAM DMR Machine, located on Cheyenne Mountain above Colorado Springs This machine sits atop Cheyenne Mountain overlooking Colorado Springs and Pueblo. The talkgroups that are setup on this system are the Fun Machine Analog transcoded and statically linked on TS1 as TG310815. At this time TS2 will carry TG3108 and 3740 statically and the following are all PTTable with a 15 minute activity timeout (310,31079,31080,31082,31083,31084,31085,31086,31088,310895,311,312,31200,31203,313,31327,314,3140,31400,31408,3148,315,31563,316,31600,31601,31602,31603,31604,31605,31606,31607,31608,31609,31623,31648,31652,317,318,319,3740,91,9112,93).
